Source-code tree:

include/	: source header files (symbolic links to other directories)
intra/  	: intra/inter-cluster communication. (the name was given
				due to historical reasons and kinda of misleading)
machine/  	: machine specific operations abstration layer
mpi/  		: mpi wrapper functions
net/  		: NETD device
thread/  	: thread abstraction, using spawn/join model
ukey/  		: thread-specific data
utils/		: timer, debug, buffer manager, message queue modules
